Class JSONEntity<T>

  • java.lang.Object
    • es.ed0.tinyjson.JSONEntity<T>
  • Type Parameters:
    T - Type of key: String for JSONS, Integer for Arrays

    public abstract class JSONEntity<T>
extends java.lang.Object
implements java.lang.Iterable<java.lang.Object>
    Abstract class that defines basic functionality for JSON entities (json objects and arrays)

      • get

        public abstract java.lang.Object get(java.lang.String... keys)
        Searches for a value recursively, this is handy for getting a value inside multiple nested JSONObjects
        Example: JSONObject json = json1:{key1:"value0",json2:{json3:{key2:"false",value:"I'm a value!"}}}
        json.get("json1", "json2", "json3", "value"); Would return "I'm a value!", or null if any of the nodes was not found
        Parameters:
        keys - Ordered keys
        Returns:
        Object mapped by last key
